SP.P:
You shall be us'd with as much respect as
myself—She has here inform'd me, you're unfor∣tunate;
but the particulars I am ignorant of.

I am already satisfy'd of my misfortunes;
therefore, curiosity might betray me to a knowledge
that, perhaps, wou'd heighten 'em.

Nay, now here's a more convincing proof;
this is the very door tht opens into one of my
rooms!
